methods.equals:
Helper method for implementing Object.equals(Object).

:param aArray: (io.deephaven.engine.tables.dbarrays.BooleanVector) - The LHS of the equality test (always a BooleanVector)
:param b: (java.lang.Object) - The RHS of the equality test
:return: (boolean) Whether the two inputs are equal
methods.getDirect:
Return a version of this Vector that is flattened out to only reference memory.

methods.hashCode:
Helper method for implementing Object.hashCode(). Follows the pattern in
 Arrays.hashCode(Object[]).

:param array: (io.deephaven.engine.tables.dbarrays.BooleanVector) - The BooleanVector to hash
:return: (int) The hash code
methods.toString:
Helper method for implementing Object.toString().

:param array: (io.deephaven.engine.tables.dbarrays.BooleanVector) - The BooleanVector to convert to a String
